<p>
  <u>Bannari Amman Institute of Technology</u> is an engineering college located in 
  <i>Sathyamangalam, Erode, Tamil Nadu, India</i>. It was founded by the Bannari Amman Group 
  in 1996 and is affiliated to Anna University. The institute offers 21 undergraduate, 
  10 postgraduate programmes in Engineering, Technology and Management studies. 
  All the departments of Engineering and Technology are recognized by Anna University, 
  Chennai to offer Ph.D. programmes.
</p>

